'''GameMaker'''（最初为'''Animo'''，2011年之前为'''Game Maker'''）是一个系列[[跨平台|跨平台]][[游戏引擎|游戏引擎]]，由{{le|Mark Overmars}}于1999年创建，2007年后由{{le|YoYo Games}}开发。最新的版本是2017年发布的GameMaker Studio 2。

GameMaker支持使用自定义拖放式[[視覺化程式設計語言|视觉化编程语言]]或称为Game Maker Language的[[脚本语言|脚本语言]]创建[[跨平台|跨平台]]和多类型的[[电子游戏|电子游戏]]。该语言可用于开发拖放功能无法创建的更加高级的游戏。GameMaker最初的设计目的是让新手[[程序员|程序员]]能够在没有太多编程知识的情况下制作游戏。最新版本的软件也开始注重吸引高级开发人员。<ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=dM-9CgAAQBAJ&pg=PA3 |title=The GameMaker Standard |last1=Vinciguerra |first1=David |last2=Howell |first2=Andrew |date=16 October 2015 |publisher=CRC Press |isbn=978-1-317-51469-5 |access-date=2022-03-22 |archive-date=2020-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610114430/https://books.google.com/books?id=dM-9CgAAQBAJ&pg=PA3 }}</ref>

== 概述 ==
GameMaker主要用于制作拥有2D图形的游戏，允许[[开箱即用|开箱即用]]的[[位图|位图]]、[[矢量图形|矢量图形]]（SWF）<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/309594/GameMaker_Studio_2_gets_new_lowcost_Creators_Edition.php |title=GameMaker Studio 2 gets new low-cost 'Creators Edition' |last=Kerr |first=Chris |access-date=9 May 2018 |language=en |archive-date=2021-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210826102330/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/309594/GameMaker_Studio_2_gets_new_lowcost_Creators_Edition.php }}</ref>和2D[[骨骼动画|骨骼动画]]（Esoteric Software的Spine）<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.yoyogames.com/blog/43/skeletal-animation-sprites-using-spine|title=Skeletal Animation Sprites Using Spine {{!}} Blog {{!}} YoYo Games|website=Yoyo Games|language=en|access-date=9 May 2018|archive-date=2019-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190601133948/https://www.yoyogames.com/blog/43/skeletal-animation-sprites-using-spine}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.brokenjoysticks.net/2017/03/12/game-maker-studio-takes-on-titans/|title=GDC17: GameMaker Studios 2.0 Takes On Industry Titans {{!}} Broken Joysticks|date=12 March 2017|work=Broken Joysticks|access-date=9 May 2018|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180907195535/https://www.brokenjoysticks.net/2017/03/12/game-maker-studio-takes-on-titans/}}</ref>以及用于绘制图形的大型标准库。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://docs2.yoyogames.com/source/_build/3_scripting/4_gml_reference/drawing/index.html |title=Drawing |website=docs2.yoyogames.com |access-date=9 May 2018 |archive-date=2021-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210823100510/http://docs2.yoyogames.com/source/_build/3_scripting/4_gml_reference/drawing/index.html }}</ref>
尽管软件允许用户有限地使用[[三维计算机图形|3D图形]]，但其形式为{{Le|顶点缓冲区|Vertex buffer}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://docs2.yoyogames.com/source/_build/3_scripting/4_gml_reference/drawing/primitives/index.html |title=Drawing And Creating Primitives |website=docs2.yoyogames.com |access-date=9 May 2018 |archive-date=2021-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210614002243/https://docs2.yoyogames.com/source/_build/3_scripting/4_gml_reference/drawing/primitives/index.html }}</ref>和[[矩阵|矩阵]]函数，因此并不适合新手用户。

该引擎在Windows、UWP和Xbox One上使用[[Direct3D|Direct3D]]；在macOS和Linux上使用[[OpenGL|OpenGL]]；在Android和iOS上使用[[OpenGL_ES|OpenGL ES]]；在HTML5上使用[[WebGL|WebGL]]或[[Canvas_(HTML元素)|2D Canvas]]，在[[電子遊戲機|游戏主机]]上使用专有API。

该引擎的主要元素之一是带有[[位图|光栅图形]]、[[關卡_(電子遊戲)|關卡]]设计、脚本、[[路径_(计算机科学)|路径]]和[[着色器|着色器]]（[[GLSL|GLSL]]或[[高级着色器语言|HLSL]]）编辑器的IDE。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.macrumors.com/2017/09/02/gamemaker-studio-2-debuts-on-macos/ |title=2D Game Development Engine 'GameMaker Studio 2' Debuts on macOS |access-date=9 May 2018 |language=en |archive-date=2022-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220325044921/https://www.macrumors.com/2017/09/02/gamemaker-studio-2-debuts-on-macos/ }}</ref>其他功能可以通过软件的脚本语言或特定平台的本地拓展来实现。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://venturebeat.com/2017/05/23/gamemaker-studio-2-gets-an-education-edition/ |title=GameMaker Studio 2 gets an education edition |date=23 May 2017 |work=VentureBeat |access-date=9 May 2018 |language=en-US |archive-date=2022-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220322144957/https://venturebeat.com/2017/05/23/gamemaker-studio-2-gets-an-education-edition/ }}</ref>在GameMaker Studio 2中，你可以选择将游戏导出为[[Nullsoft腳本安裝系統|NSIS]]安装包，或导出为包含游戏data.win文件和编辑器“包含的文件”选项卡中的所有文件的[[ZIP格式|.zip]]文件。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://docs2.yoyogames.com/source/_build/1_overview/2_quick_start/6_compiling.html|title=Compiling|website=docs2.yoyogames.com|access-date=2019-02-20|archive-date=2021-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211109183609/https://docs2.yoyogames.com/source/_build/1_overview/2_quick_start/6_compiling.html}}</ref>

