=== 拖拽放置 ===
拖拽放置（Drag and Drop，DnD）是GameMaker的可视化脚本工具。

DnD允许执行常见的开发人员命令（例如实例化对象、调用函数、处理文件和数据结构）而无需编写代码，拖拽放置主要针对新手用户。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thisisxbox.com/interview-james-cox-yoyo-games-gamemaker-studio-2/|title=Interview: James Cox of YoYo Games about GameMaker Studio 2 {{!}} This Is Xbox|work=This Is Xbox|access-date=9 May 2018|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200106074455/http://www.thisisxbox.com/interview-james-cox-yoyo-games-gamemaker-studio-2/}}</ref>

虽然从历史上看，DnD能在轻松完成的事情上的使用相当有限，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Drag-and-Drop icons to GameMaker Language reference|url=https://www.packtpub.com/sites/default/files/downloads/4100OT_Appendix_Drag_and_drop_Icons_to_GameMaker_Language_Reference.pdf|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2017-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223025538/https://www.packtpub.com/sites/default/files/downloads/4100OT_Appendix_Drag_and_drop_Icons_to_GameMaker_Language_Reference.pdf}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/no-coding-required-how-new-designers-are-using-gamemaker-to-create-indie-smash-hits/|title=No coding required: How new designers are using GameMaker to create indie smash hits|work=pcgamer|access-date=9 May 2018|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220421191825/https://www.pcgamer.com/no-coding-required-how-new-designers-are-using-gamemaker-to-create-indie-smash-hits/}}</ref>但GameMaker Studio 2对该系统进行了彻底的改进，能够使用DnD完成更多的任务，并将其直接转换为代码（为有兴趣迁移到代码的用户提供IDE内预览）。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://venturebeat.com/2017/09/03/gamemaker-studio-creators-look-back-at-17-years-of-development/|title=GameMaker Studio creators look back at 17 years of development|date=4 September 2017|work=VentureBeat|access-date=9 May 2018|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180908003154/https://venturebeat.com/2017/09/03/gamemaker-studio-creators-look-back-at-17-years-of-development/}}</ref>

== GameMaker语言 ==
GameMaker语言是GameMaker的脚本语言。这是一种[[指令式編程|指令式]]、[[动态类型|动态类型]]的，类似[[JavaScript|JavaScript]]和[[C语言|C语言]]的语言。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=eDzlCwAAQBAJ&pg=PR6|title=GameMaker Programming By Example|last1=Christian|first1=Brian|last2=Isaacs|first2=Steven|date=28 December 2015|publisher=Packt Publishing Ltd|isbn=978-1-78588-847-2|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2022-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324030102/https://books.google.com/books?id=eDzlCwAAQBAJ&pg=PR6}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-5OFAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA9|title=Getting Started with Game Maker|last=Jr|first=Jerry Lee Ford|date=1 June 2009|publisher=Cengage Learning|isbn=978-1435455214|language=en|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2022-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324030102/https://books.google.com/books?id=-5OFAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA9}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=PLdsEjKnt5AC&pg=PA225|title=The Game Maker's Apprentice: Game Development for Beginners|last1=Habgood|first1=Jacob|last2=Overmars|first2=Mark|date=31 December 2006|publisher=Apress|isbn=978-1-4302-0159-5|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2022-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324030100/https://books.google.com/books?id=PLdsEjKnt5AC&pg=PA225}}</ref>

该语言在本机平台上的默认操作模式通过[[堆栈|堆栈机]]实现；它也可以通过[[LLVM|LLVM]][[源到源编译器|编译]]为C++源码以提高性能。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.adweek.com/digital/gamemaker-studio-introduces-yoyo-compiler-and-cross-platform-shader-support/|title=GameMaker: Studio introduces YoYo Compiler and cross-platform Shader support|access-date=9 May 2018|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181218173259/https://www.adweek.com/digital/gamemaker-studio-introduces-yoyo-compiler-and-cross-platform-shader-support/}}</ref>在HTML5上，GML是源到源编译成JavaScript的，在非调试版本中实现了优化和[[極簡化|压缩]]。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=uDWG1gYWxokC|title=HTML5 Game Development with GameMaker|last=Elliott|first=Jason Lee|date=22 April 2013|publisher=Packt Publishing Ltd|isbn=978-1-84969-411-7|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2022-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324030103/https://books.google.com/books?id=uDWG1gYWxokC}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
GameMaker最初由{{Le|Mark Overmars|Mark Overmars}}开发。该软件于1999年11月15日以Animo的名义首次发布（当时，它只是一个具有有限视觉脚本功能的图形工具）。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-5OFAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA5|title=Getting Started with Game Maker|last=Jr|first=Jerry Lee Ford|date=1 June 2009|publisher=Cengage Learning|isbn=978-1435455214|language=en|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2022-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324030101/https://books.google.com/books?id=-5OFAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA5}}</ref>该软件的第一个版本是在[[Delphi|Delphi]]上开发的。<ref>{{cite web|title=Game Maker Studio engine|url=http://www.desura.com/engines/game-maker|access-date=29 May 2013|publisher=Desura|archive-date=2013-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130519170952/http://www.desura.com/engines/game-maker}}</ref>

在随后的版本中，该软件更名为Game Maker，同时也朝着更通用的2D游戏开发方向发展。

5.0版及以下版本为[[免費軟體|免費軟體]]；5.1版本引入了可选注册费用；5.3版为注册用户引入了许多新功能，包括[[粒子系统|粒子系统]]、网络以及使用DLL扩展游戏内容的可能性。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Game Maker Pages|url=http://www.gamemaker.nl:80/registration.html|access-date=8 May 2018|date=10 January 2004|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040110215821/http://www.gamemaker.nl:80/registration.html|archive-date=10 January 2004|url-status=dead}}</ref>

6.4版（2004年10月）引入了有限的3D图形使用功能，并同时将运行时的绘图通道从{{Le|可视组件库|Visual Component Library}}迁移至[[DirectX|DirectX]]。<ref name=":0">{{cite book|title=Getting Started with Game Maker|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0cs4Jv7ik5gC&pg=PA11|last=Ford|first=Jerry|publisher=Course Technology, a part of Cengage Learning|year=2010|isbn=978-1-59863-882-0|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2022-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220407215744/https://books.google.com/books?id=0cs4Jv7ik5gC&pg=PA11}}</ref>

公众越来越大的专注度促使Overmars寻求帮助来扩大项目，并于2007年与YoYo Games建立了合作关系。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=NUFIBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA341|title=A Brief History Of Video Games: From Atari to Virtual Reality|last=Stanton|first=Rich|date=23 July 2015|publisher=Little, Brown Book Group|isbn=9781472118813|language=en|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2022-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324030101/https://books.google.com/books?id=NUFIBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA341}}</ref>从那时起，开发工作由YoYo Games负责，而Overmars则继续担任公司董事之一。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=PLdsEjKnt5AC&pg=PR16|title=The Game Maker's Apprentice: Game Development for Beginners|last1=Habgood|first1=Jacob|last2=Overmars|first2=Mark|date=31 December 2006|publisher=Apress|isbn=978-1-4302-0159-5|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2022-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324030107/https://books.google.com/books?id=PLdsEjKnt5AC&pg=PR16}}</ref>7.0版是在此合作关系下发布的第一个版本。

第一个兼容macOS的版本于2009年发行，<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-5OFAwAAQBAJ&pg=PR14|title=Getting Started with Game Maker|last=Jr|first=Jerry Lee Ford|date=1 June 2009|publisher=Cengage Learning|isbn=978-1435455214|language=en|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2022-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324030104/https://books.google.com/books?id=-5OFAwAAQBAJ&pg=PR14}}</ref>只需要稍作改动即可在两个操作系统上制作游戏。

8.1版（2011年4月）将软件名称改为GameMaker（无空格）<ref>{{cite web|title=The Original Game-Maker|url=http://www.diygamer.com/2010/04/original-gamemaker/|access-date=15 January 2015|date=30 April 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140301005957/http://www.diygamer.com/2010/04/original-gamemaker/|archive-date=1 March 2014|last1=Eric-Jon Rössel|first1=Tairne}}</ref>以避免与1991年的软件''{{Le|Game-Maker|Game-Maker}}''混淆。该版本还用C++重写了运行时，<ref name=":1">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5UAIAAAAQBAJ|title=Getting Started with Game Maker|last=Ford|first=Jerry|date=2009|publisher=Cengage Learning|isbn=978-1133168966|page=333|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2022-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324030101/https://books.google.com/books?id=5UAIAAAAQBAJ}}</ref>{{failed verification|date=July 2020}}以解决之前版本的性能问题。

2011年9月“GameMaker: HTML5”首次发布——这是一个全新的软件，能够将桌面游戏和浏览器游戏一并导出。<ref name="Rose">{{Cite news|url=https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/37398/YoYo_Games_Releases_GameMaker_HTML5_Tools.php|title=YoYo Games Releases GameMaker: HTML5 Tools|last=Rose|first=Mike|access-date=8 May 2018|language=en|archive-date=2022-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324030105/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/37398/YoYo_Games_Releases_GameMaker_HTML5_Tools.php}}</ref>

GameMaker: Studio于2012年3月进入公测阶段，<ref name="Rose" />并与2012年5月全面发布。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://venturebeat.com/2012/05/22/yoyo-games-unveils-gamemaker-studio-for-cross-platform-development/|title=YoYo Games unveils GameMaker: Studio for cross-platform development|date=22 May 2012|work=VentureBeat|access-date=8 May 2018|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324030105/https://venturebeat.com/2012/05/22/yoyo-games-unveils-gamemaker-studio-for-cross-platform-development/}}</ref>最初支持的平台包括Windows、Mac、HTML5、Android和iOS。在接下来的几年里引入了其他平台和功能；<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://csanyk.com/2012/09/game-maker-studio-1-1-released/|title=Game Maker Studio 1.1 released - csanyk.com|date=6 September 2012|work=csanyk.com|access-date=8 May 2018|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630000213/https://csanyk.com/2012/09/game-maker-studio-1-1-released/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://venturebeat.com/2013/08/27/yoyo-games-updates-its-game-tools-to-speed-development-time/|title=YoYo Games updates GameMaker: Studio to speed development time|date=27 August 2013|work=VentureBeat|access-date=8 May 2018|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324030102/https://venturebeat.com/2013/08/27/yoyo-games-updates-its-game-tools-to-speed-development-time/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://jeux.developpez.com/actu/71823/GameMaker-est-disponible-en-version-1-3-et-apporte-un-nouveau-debogueur-et-le-support-des-consoles-de-Sony/|title=GameMaker est disponible en version 1.3 et apporte un nouveau débogueur et le support des consoles de Sony|work=Developpez.com|access-date=8 May 2018|language=fr|archive-date=2021-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210822223349/https://jeux.developpez.com/actu/71823/GameMaker-est-disponible-en-version-1-3-et-apporte-un-nouveau-debogueur-et-le-support-des-consoles-de-Sony/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Welcome to GameMaker: Studio 1.4 {{!}} GameMaker Blog|url=http://www.gamemakerblog.net/welcome-to-gamemaker-studio-1-4/|access-date=8 May 2018|date=18 June 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160618133327/http://www.gamemakerblog.net/welcome-to-gamemaker-studio-1-4/|archive-date=18 June 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref>2012年末，一些正版用户遇到了反盗版措施失灵的事故。<ref>{{cite web|title=Gamemaker anti-piracy bug destroys developer assets | Game Development | News by Develop|url=http://www.develop-online.net/news/42651/GameMaker-fixes-anti-piracy-bug-afflicting-users|access-date=28 April 2019|date=29 November 2012|last=Chapple|first=Craig|website=Develop|publisher=Intent Media|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130127181539/http://www.develop-online.net/news/42651/GameMaker-fixes-anti-piracy-bug-afflicting-users|archive-date=27 January 2013|url-status=dead}}</ref>

2015年2月，{{Le|Playtech|Playtech}}和{{Le|YoYo Games|YoYo Games}}收购了GameMaker，该公告再次声明，GameMaker将会进一步改进，这些计划吸引了更多的用户，其中包括更多的高级开发者。<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=YoYo Games is Acquired by Playtech plc {{!}} YoYo Games|url=http://www.yoyogames.com/playtech|access-date=8 May 2018|date=26 March 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326191637/http://www.yoyogames.com/playtech|archive-date=26 March 2015|url-status=dead}}</ref>

2016年11月，GameMaker Studio 2的Beta版首次发布，<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.pcgamesn.com/gamemaker-studio-2-beta|title=GameMaker Studio 2 enters beta|work=PCGamesN|access-date=8 May 2018|archive-date=2022-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324030103/https://www.pcgamesn.com/gamemaker-studio-2-beta}}</ref>完整版于2017年3月发布。<ref>{{Cite web|title=GameMaker Studio 2 Released|url=http://www.gamefromscratch.com/post/2017/03/09/GameMaker-Studio-2-Released.aspx|access-date=8 May 2018|last=GameFromScratch.com|first=Copyright|website=www.gamefromscratch.com|archive-date=2018-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180731123812/http://www.gamefromscratch.com/post/2017/03/09/GameMaker-Studio-2-Released.aspx}}</ref>这个版本展示了一个完全重新设计的IDE（使用C#编写<ref>{{Cite web|title=GameMaker Studio 2: Remade to Stay Up-to-date - Gamesauce: Global Inspiration for Game Developers|url=http://www.gamesauce.biz/2017/04/05/gamemaker-studio-2-remade-stay-date/|access-date=8 May 2018|website=www.gamesauce.biz|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190905171611/http://www.gamesauce.biz/2017/04/05/gamemaker-studio-2-remade-stay-date/}}</ref>），以及一些新的编辑工具和运行时功能。

2020年8月，主要更新2.3版本发布，为IDE、运行时和脚本语言带来了大量的新功能。<ref>{{cite web|title=YoYo Games launches GameMaker Studio 2 version 2.3|url=https://europeangaming.eu/portal/latest-news/2020/08/20/76397/yoyo-games-launches-gamemaker-studio-2-version-2-3/|date=20 August 2020|website=European Gaming Industry News|last1=Miller|first1=George}}</ref>

2021年1月，{{Le|YoYo Games|YoYo Games}}以1000万[[美元|美元]]的价格出售给[[Opera軟件|Opera軟件]]。GameMaker的开发团队保持不变，没有对GameMaker Studio进行过任何重大的开发更改。<ref>{{cite web|title=Opera bought the owner of GameMaker for its new gaming division – Destructoid|url=https://www.destructoid.com/stories/opera-bought-the-owner-of-gamemaker-for-its-new-gaming-division-617344.phtml|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2021-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419085421/https://www.destructoid.com/stories/opera-bought-the-owner-of-gamemaker-for-its-new-gaming-division-617344.phtml}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Opera acquires YoYo Games for $10 million and launches Opera Gaming division {{!}} VentureBeat|url=https://venturebeat.com/2021/01/20/opera-acquires-yoyo-games-for-10-million-and-launches-opera-gaming-division/|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303221354/https://venturebeat.com/2021/01/20/opera-acquires-yoyo-games-for-10-million-and-launches-opera-gaming-division/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Opera Acquires YoYo Games, Launches Opera Gaming|url=https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/opera-acquires-yoyo-games-launches-opera-gaming-301211728.html|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2022-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324030100/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/opera-acquires-yoyo-games-launches-opera-gaming-301211728.html}}</ref>

2021年8月，YoYo Games声称他们正在改变许可证策略，并会提供一个免费版本的GameMaker引擎。<ref>{{cite web|title=oYo Games streamlines GameMaker licenses, offers new free version|url=https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2021-08-10-yoyo-games-streamlines-gamemaker-licenses-offers-new-free-version|website=gamesindustry.biz|publisher=Gamer Network Limited, a ReedPop company|last1=Dealessandri|first1=Marie|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2022-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220426104927/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2021-08-10-yoyo-games-streamlines-gamemaker-licenses-offers-new-free-version}}</ref>

== 反响 ==
根据223条用户评论，该项目目前在[[Mod_DB|Mod DB]]上的评分为8.5/10；许多人认为它的灵活性和易用性是积极的，而不稳定、崩溃、项目过老和过时的功能则是消极的。<ref>{{cite web|title=GameMaker: Studio Reviews|url=http://www.indiedb.com/engines/gamemaker/reviews|access-date=15 January 2015|publisher=DBolical Pty Ltd.|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804145727/https://www.indiedb.com/engines/gamemaker/reviews}}</ref> 《独立游戏杂志》（''Indie Game Magazine''）的Douglas Clements写到，该软件“简化了游戏的开发流程”，并且“对于初学者来书十分友好，但在开发过程中又足够强大”，但同时他又指出“{{如何翻譯|resource objects have to be gathered if unable to create}}”，并且“[[Steam|Steam]]和YoYo Games网站之间的授权‘粗综复杂’”。<ref>{{cite web|title='GameMaker: Studio' – Lord Over The Pixels|url=http://indiegamemag.com/gamemaker-studio-lord-over-the-pixels/|access-date=19 January 2017|author=Douglas Clements|website=Indie Games Magazine|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222224901/http://indiegamemag.com/gamemaker-studio-lord-over-the-pixels/|archive-date=22 December 2017}}</ref>

